<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DSSearch API Server</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      color: #666666;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <h1>DSSearch API Server</h1>
  <p>This is the API server for the DSSearch application. For more information, please visit the GitHub project page.</p>
  <a href="https://github.com/Joinsider/DSSearch/" target="_blank">Visit DSSearch on GitHub</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>